Package sheet4.a_linkedTuple Description

Tests for Sheet 4 Task A: LinkedNaturalNumberTuple. Run LinkedNaturalNumberTupleTest to test your implementation of the LinkedNaturalNumberTuple. Run InteractiveConsoleTest to test your interactive console.
